channel.title: EyfiaScape Release Construction ll Summoning ll Dungeoneering & More!
channel.description:
The Reason im releasing this is because alot of people have been asking for it. :) I dont own any of these. Im releasing it for the people that want it.
Credits : IntdubPk Client, RuneFx owner, And Eyfia. :) ----------------------------------------------------
Download Links:
Client: http://dl.dropbox.com/u/21487126/EyfiaScape2/EyfiaScape-Client.zip Server: http://dl.dropbox.com/u/21487126/EyfiaScape2/EyfiaScape-Server.zip Cache: http://dl.dropbox.com/u/21487126/EyfiaScape2/EyfiaScapeCache.zip
Features: Summoning, Dungeoneering, and all other skills working! Summoning familiars, pets Charms from monsters, and Summoning shop 3 fully completeable quests 27 fully completeable achievements Construction skill, building stuff Full GWD with Nex! Custom mini-games Dupe fixes Overloads New gameframe etc. Changed a lot interfaces to better ones Dungeoneering with NPCs, killcount, rewards shop! GWD and Dungeoneering NPCs Dungeoneering and new GWD items Pest Control with rewards shop Hunter with implings and looting Mage Bank with rewards shop JAD (Fire cape) Corporeal Beast Evil Spirit (Wildy boss) King Black Dragon Barrelchest guardian Gnome and Wildy agility course All RC altars All skillcape emotes working (Dung too!) Better bank, shop, trade etc. interfaces Working GS, SS, PvP, SoL and other weapon specs Pk, Mage Bank, Multi PvP, Fun PK Sprit Shields with effects! DFS special Full PvP, Primal, Promethium, Zephyrium, Torva, Virtus, Pernix, Dragon (g), Soulbell and more armors with correct stats Some great and awesome shops! Custom Donator zone with shops, skilling and monsters And even more that I can't remember
For Media, Go Here: http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,534976.0.html
[size=14pt]NOTE: Sacred Pk is a much more advance version of eyfiascape. eyfia, is the base i believe.[/size]
Download, Enjoy, And Have Fun. No need to flame..If you dont want it, dont download.
